Add an Equation

\[ f(x) = \beta_0 + \beta_1 x + \beta_2 x^2 + \beta_3 x^3 + \beta_4 (x-\xi)^3_+ \]

\[ (x-\xi)^3_+ = \begin{cases} (x-\xi)^3\, ,& x>\xi \\ 0 ,& x\leq\xi \end{cases} \]

\[ \begin{aligned} (x \leq \xi) \Rightarrow f(x) &= \beta_0 + \beta_1 x + \beta_2 x^2 + \beta_3 x^3 \\ (x > \xi) \Rightarrow f(x) &= \beta_0 + \beta_1 x + \beta_2 x^2 + \beta_3 x^3 + \beta_4(x^3 -3x^2\xi + 3x\xi^2 - \xi^3) \\ &=(\beta_0 + \beta_4\xi^3) + (\beta_1 + 3\beta_4\xi^2)x + (\beta_2 - 3\beta_4) \end{aligned} \]
